{"tid":480864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友一齊好辛苦","createTime":"2017-11-26T14:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T15:14:41.000Z","uid":38293,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bdff9876e6363a7f12e52d3b58922c6afa4d10f3","tid":480864,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"佢咩時候都喺到玩電話<br />\n食飯又玩 行街又行 上次見家長都只係放底過部電話幾秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我頭先終於忍唔住唔佢啦 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> me. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男朋友<br />\nme:其實你想點㗎？我哋一齊咗3個月啦，頭一個月都好哋哋，我嚟m你會關心我，而家呢？你連句安慰說話都唔講<br />\n男朋友：唔？嗯！嗯嗯！(望住電話)<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得得閒玩吓係無問題囉，但佢根本玩到入魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且佢最近近視又加深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺個得心好空虛，我好攰， 好似湊仔咁呀<br />\n<br />\n我真係好擔心佢工作時嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba70f559d80388f078b715ac2b00bf80ae4c89f","tid":480864,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"接受唔到咪分手囉，臭G"},{"pid":"fc9c68a0f21fc6645dc3d57f90d14a72c650611b","tid":480864,"uid":151337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢咩時候都喺到玩電話<br />\n食飯又玩 行街又行 上次見家長都只係放底過部電話幾秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我頭先終於忍唔住唔佢啦 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> me. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男朋友<br />\nme:其實你想點㗎？我哋一齊咗3個月啦，頭一個月都好哋哋，我嚟m你會關心我，而家呢？你連句安慰說話都唔講<br />\n男朋友：唔？嗯！嗯嗯！(望住電話)<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得得閒玩吓係無問題囉，但佢根本玩到入魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且佢最近近視又加深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺個得心好空虛，我好攰， 好似湊仔咁呀<br />\n<br />\n我真係好擔心佢工作時嘅情況<img src=\"/as